:

1. *Oprosti* mi ovaj put. (Forgive me this time.) 
2. Želim ti da *oprostiš* sve što ti je učinjeno. (I wish you to forgive everything that was done to you.)
3. Želim da *oprostiš* sebi. (I want you to forgive yourself.)
4. Očekujem da ćeš mi *oprostiti* za sve što sam uradio. (I expect you to forgive me for everything I have done.)
5. *Oprosti* nam greške. (Forgive us our mistakes.)